Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:12.38,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ふたりでひとつのような僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:22.11,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}翼広げ　羽ばたく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.31,0:01:21.04,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}曾追寻的世界尽头  现已在脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:25.42,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深深绝望  渐渐消解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:31.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}人间憎恶日积月累  终难以承受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:36.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}喷涌而出  流入心胸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:43.28,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何需畏惧身之污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:48.15,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不再踌躇  Try to dive in now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:54.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Get all the free and dream  只要和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:59.39,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无光暗夜终将消散
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.61,0:02:05.25,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Get all the free and dream  穿越无尽时空
